    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.abs((wp.sin(tmp + 0.92) - v1))
    v2 = wp.abs((wp.cos(tmp + 0.06) - (v0 + 0.34 / v1 + 0.03)))
    tmp = (((tmp + 0.04 / v2 + 0.04) + (v1 + 0.19 - v0 + 0.07)) - (v0 + (tmp + 0.72 - v2 + 0.00)))
    v0 = v0
    v2 = 0.05
    v2 = wp.cos(wp.exp(wp.abs(v1 + 0.43)))
    data[tid] = v0
